title: [Stream] Climbing from Diamond 3 to Master

embed.description: Diamond Solo Queue | Come join Camp Burrito! | Best Burrito AU

body:
Hello friends.

Tomorrow I am going to be streaming solo queue, Ranked 5s and maybe some normal games for roughly 7 hours. The majority of it will be climbing from Diamond 3 to Master in Solo Queue with a Silver Ranked Team on the side. The stream will go from around 2 PM AEST to around 7 PM AEST 30/10/2015. Feel free to drop in and hang around and give me advice on how to make the stream more entertaining.

http://www.twitch.tv/best_burrito_au

replies.body: Something's come up so the stream's cancelled. I doubt anyone was going to watch but sorry regardless.
